/*

Purpose:			

Parameters:			

Return Value:		

Date		Who		Reason
22 Sep 2023 navhl20 ChangeRequest 60640:[60641] EUP | Mobile DD - Packing Jobs

*/

vars

begin
	/*We only showing packing child jobs for pack load by request*/
